&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work cross-functionally to drive nonclinical safety related activities from discovery through regulatory filings and to commercialization for various programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and oversee the execution of phase appropriate nonclinical safety strategies along with integrated project plans including milestones, timelines, resources and budgets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate interactions with CRO&#39;s, in collaboration with the Nonclinical Development Operations group, to ensure delivery of study results and reports consistent with program timelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide strategic contribution as the subject matter expert for GLP, non-GLP, and safety pharmacology studies supporting development and platform programs.&lt;/li&gt;
