&lt;li&gt;Define and execute the QC testing, method strategy, and technical execution to enable next‑generation autologous cell therapy manufacturing processes, including analytical readiness for process validation, comparability, and technology transfer.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and coordinate analytical method transfer, qualification, and validation activities across internal and external QC laboratories, ensuring compliant, phase‑appropriate, and inspection‑ready execution.&lt;/li&gt;
