&lt;li&gt;Negotiate directly with&amp;nbsp;Commercial&amp;nbsp;and Government&amp;nbsp;Payers&amp;nbsp;to ensure pricing and coverage for the Beam portfolio, potentially including managed Medicaid and Medicaid FFS.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educate providers on local payer trends, appropriate billing and coding for gene therapy, providing support to offices for individual patient reimbursement journeys, including troubleshooting reimbursement concerns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor, analyze, and influence local payer trends in rare disease and gene therapy to ensure environment supports innovation&amp;nbsp;in gene therapy affordability and accessibility.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide training and education programs on reimbursement best practices and health policy issues to internal stakeholders and external stakeholders, such as Treatment Centers.&lt;/li&gt;
