&lt;li&gt;Maintain living account profiles and strategic account plans, updated quarterly and aligned to brand strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage senior institutional leadership in strategic conversations about the value and operational integration of Beam’s therapies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
