&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Demand Generation, Utilization &amp;amp; Insights&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive appropriate, label-compliant therapy utilization within assigned accounts, consistently meeting or exceeding demand targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze account performance to identify utilization trends, referral gaps, and opportunities to optimize pathway efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Beam at national and regional conferences, including Thought Leader engagement and reporting on relevant sessions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
